Note that the thermo model itself is not returned as this class could be substituted in the hierarcy for one which mirrors the functionality, but does not include a thermo model; an incompressible phase model, for example

Only when the cells are actually visited does it need the results to be present. It is expected that there is little benefit to be gained from doing this on a patch by patch basis since the number of processor interfaces is quite small and the overhead of checking whether a processor interface is finished might be quite high (call into mpi).
